<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>404 — Page Not Found</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/retro.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/lucide-static@latest/font/lucide.min.css">
  <style>.i { font-family: 'lucide'; font-style: normal; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: -2px; margin-right: 3px; }</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="auth-container">
    <div class="xp-window auth-window" style="width:500px;">
      <div class="xp-titlebar" style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, #E0734C 0%, #C0513A 100%);">
        <span class="xp-titlebar__title"><i class="i">&#xe3a3;</i> 404 — File Not Found</span>
        <div class="xp-titlebar__buttons">
          <button class="xp-titlebar__btn">_</button>
          <button class="xp-titlebar__btn">□</button>
          <button class="xp-titlebar__btn xp-titlebar__btn--close">✕</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="xp-window__body text-center">
        
        <div class="under-construction" style="padding:15px 0;">
          <h1 class="text-red text-pixel" style="font-size:42px;">Internet Explorer</h1>
          <h2 class="text-pixel" style="font-size:24px; color:#555;">HTTP 404 - File Not Found</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="inset-panel" style="text-align:left; font-size:12px; line-height:1.6; background:#fff;">
          <p><strong>The page you are looking for might have been removed, had its name changed, or is temporarily unavailable.</strong></p>
          <hr style="border:1px groove #999; margin:8px 0;">
          <p>Please try the following:</p>
          <ul style="margin-left:20px; margin-top:6px;">
            <li>If you typed the page address in the Address bar, make sure that it is spelled correctly.</li>
            <li>Click the <a href="javascript:history.back()">Back</a> button to try another link.</li>
            <li>Go to the <a href="/home">Homepage</a> to search for your friends.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top:15px;">
          <a href="/home" class="xp-btn xp-btn--primary"><i class="i">&#xe4b6;</i> Back to Safety</a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-md text-small text-muted">
          <i class="i">&#xe5b7;</i> Powered by Windows XP SP2 & IIS 6.0
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script src="/js/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
